{"tid":866327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼倡公園懸掛國旗　從日常生活培養民族感情","createTime":"2018-10-17T18:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T16:41:44.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"859abcc0d1c7a30ba0aade974fba6cfefeb35f24","tid":866327,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T18:39:09.000Z","msg":"民建聯主席李慧琼近日在《星島日報》專欄，提出要從日常生活推進歷史教育，效法西方國家就會在主要公園懸掛國旗，「潤物細無聲，這些做法都值得特區政府借鑑，也是當局有需要急起直追的地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/35344614_10160341908875265_796434696438284288_o_85xv6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F35344614_10160341908875265_796434696438284288_o_85xv6_1200x0.png&h=d8c5f872&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n李慧琼在專欄中提到，九龍西補選，劉小麗被取消資格做法合理，原因劉一直提出自決。<br />\n<br />\n她說遺憾是近年香港社會，特別是年輕一代出現憑空想像，脫離現實的思潮，「特區政府亦要反思，回歸已經二十年，為何成長於特區的青年朋友，對國家的認識，以至民族感情仍然十分不足。這種現象與我們的國民教育、國史教育以至《憲法》及《基本法》教育長期未做到位有莫大關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/李慧琼倡公園懸掛國旗-從日常生活培養民族感情/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9D%8E%E6%85%A7%E7%90%BC%E5%80%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E6%87%B8%E6%8E%9B%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97-%E5%BE%9E%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%9F%B9%E9%A4%8A%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E6%84%9F%E6%83%85%2F&d=qJafdh2PD12xFIro0Oi7zGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=0f846477\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9D%8E%E6%85%A7%E7%90%BC%E5%80%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E6%87%B8%E6%8E%9B%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97-%E5%BE%9E%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%9F%B9%E9%A4%8A%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E6%84%9F%E6%83%85%2F&h=e0cd2328\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/李慧琼倡公園懸掛國旗-從日常生活培養民族感情/</a>"},{"pid":"4bf6f7b0dceb70bb375859e838a88b4523c174f5","tid":866327,"uid":18